<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title><%= title %> — ClipadorAI</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/app.css" />
</head>
<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-950 text-slate-100">
  <div class="pointer-events-none fixed inset-0 -z-10 overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute -left-24 top-0 h-80 w-80 rounded-full bg-emerald-500/10 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute -right-16 bottom-10 h-96 w-96 rounded-full bg-sky-500/10 blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-[radial-gradient(ellipse_at_top,_rgba(15,23,42,0)_0%,_rgba(2,6,23,0.9)_70%)]"></div>
  </div>

  <header class="border-b border-slate-800/80">
    <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl items-center justify-between px-4 py-4">
      <a href="/" class="text-xl tracking-tight text-emerald-400"><strong>ClipadorAI</strong></a>
      <a href="/login"
        class="rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-4 py-2 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 hover:bg-emerald-400">
        Entrar
      </a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 pb-16 pt-16 sm:pt-24">
      <p class="text-sm font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-emerald-400/80">Plataforma de conteúdo</p>
      <h1 class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-4xl leading-tight text-white sm:text-5xl">
        <strong>ClipadorAI</strong>
      </h1>
      <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-relaxed text-slate-300">
        Busque vídeos e imagens, corte em Reels de até 90s, gere matérias com IA e publique
        direto nas suas páginas do Facebook.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
        <a href="/login"
          class="rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 hover:bg-emerald-400">
          Fazer login
        </a>
        <a href="#como-funciona"
          class="rounded-lg border border-slate-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-slate-200 hover:border-slate-500 hover:text-white">
          Como funciona
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="como-funciona" class="border-t border-slate-800/80 bg-slate-950/60">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-16">
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">O que o <strong>ClipadorAI</strong> faz</h2>
        <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-slate-400">
          Do conteúdo bruto ao post no Facebook, em um fluxo simples.
        </p>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 p-5">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">01</div>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-medium text-white">Buscar</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
              Pexels, YouTube, TikTok ou link direto — encontre o material e baixe.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 p-5">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">02</div>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-medium text-white">Cortar</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
              Cortes manuais ou automáticos a cada 90s no formato 9:16 para Reels.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 p-5">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">03</div>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-medium text-white">Matéria com IA</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
              Extrai a fala do vídeo e gera legenda pronta para publicar.
            </p>
          </article>
          <article class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-800 bg-slate-900/50 p-5">
            <div class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-wider text-emerald-400">04</div>
            <h3 class="mt-3 text-lg font-medium text-white">Publicar</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-400">
              Envie Reels, fotos ou posts de texto nas páginas conectadas.
            </p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="border-t border-slate-800/80">
      <div class="mx-auto flex max-w-6xl flex-col items-start justify-between gap-6 px-4 py-16 sm:flex-row sm:items-center">
        <div>
          <h2 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white">Pronto para começar?</h2>
          <p class="mt-2 text-slate-400">Entre com sua conta e abra a fila de produção.</p>
        </div>
        <a href="/login"
          class="rounded-lg bg-emerald-500 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-950 hover:bg-emerald-400">
          Entrar no <strong>ClipadorAI</strong>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="border-t border-slate-800/80">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-4 py-6 text-sm text-slate-500">
      <p><strong class="text-emerald-400">ClipadorAI</strong> — busca, corte, matéria e publicação no Facebook.</p>
      <p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-600">Desenvolvido por Erick Vinicius · Versão 1.0</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</body>
</html>
